latestPosts.caption: Forever my favorite person to annoy and adore 😄❤️

“Behind every bride who had the best wedding ever, there’s a superhero sister making magic happen. Thank you for being my rock, my planner, my stress-buster — basically my everything ❤️

“No words will ever be enough to thank you both. You didn’t just help with my wedding — you lived every moment with me, carried my stress like it was your own, and made sure I smiled even when things got overwhelming. You were my strength, my calm, and my home through it all. I’ll never forget the way you showed up — not just as sisters, but as my biggest blessings. From the bottom of my heart, thank you for giving me the most beautiful start to this new chapter. I love you both, more than you’ll ever know. ❤️ #MySistersMyStrength #ForeverGrateful”
